  <brief_title>What is the Influence of a Different Thread Pitch Design on Bone Remodelling Around Conical Southern Oral Implants?</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Multicenter Randomized Controlled Clinical Study on Conical Southern Implants With Different Thread Pitch</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
