  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients who need more than 2 dental implants will be treated by the same implant type
      (conical 4mm diameter IBT Southern implants) but with different thread pitch design (0,6mm en
      1,0mm type). In a 3 year clinical follow up period, the bone remodelling on X-rays is
      registered around these implants. The role of the thread pitch design will be investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
