  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  At least 18 years old

          -  Periodontally-healthy or periodontally-treated patients

          -  Smokers are included

          -  All types of prosthetic indications are accepted but 2 IBT type implants with
             different threads have to be placed in one patient on the same day. Implants can be
             connected or not connected in the same jaw.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  All other contra indications for implant surgery

          -  Guided bone regeneration or use of any substitutes

          -  No implantation in regenerated or augmented bone

          -  No immediate loading cases
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
